WEBVTT

00:03:58.520 --> 00:04:00.816
It can make people feel valued,

00:04:00.840 --> 00:04:02.096
respected,

00:04:02.120 --> 00:04:03.760
honored and seen.

00:04:06.360 --> 00:04:10.960
Now I'd like for you to just think
about some of the spaces that you inhabit.

00:04:11.520 --> 00:04:15.040
And I'd like to have you think
about how they make you feel.

00:04:16.079 --> 00:04:20.656
Now, there are places
that make us feel unhappy,

00:04:20.680 --> 00:04:22.256
unhealthy

00:04:22.280 --> 00:04:23.520
or uninspiring.

00:04:24.080 --> 00:04:27.056
They may be the places that you work

00:04:27.080 --> 00:04:28.280
or where you heal

00:04:29.040 --> 00:04:30.280
or even where you live.